OL,3,CGuernsey will not send national
OL,4,Cfootball teams to the Island Games
OL,6,FThe Guernsey Football Association is
OL,7,Fwithdrawing its men's and women's
OL,8,Fteams from the 2025 Island Games
OL,9,Fcompetition in Orkney.
OL,11,FThe announcement from GFA's Chief
OL,12,FExecutive, Gary Roberts, cites issues
OL,13,Fconfirming "suitable arrangements for
OL,14,Ftravel and accommodation" for players.
OL,16,FAs teams would travel with several
OL,17,Funder-18s alongside adult players, the
OL,18,FGFA would need "additional
OL,19,Fsafeguarding chaperones" who could not
OL,20,Fbe easily accommodated.
