OL,3,CGuernsey will not send national
OL,4,Cfootball teams to the Island Games
OL,6,FGary explains: "We appreciate that
OL,7,FOrkney has very limited hotel
OL,8,Faccommodation and that the organising
OL,9,Fcommittee has been doing everything
OL,10,Fpossible to increase capacity by
OL,11,Fsetting up temporary accommodation in
OL,12,Fschool buildings.
OL,14,F"Unfortunately, the accommodation we
OL,15,Fhave been allocated does not allow us
OL,16,Fto meet our responsibilities when
OL,17,Ftravelling with two teams of mixed
OL,18,Fages."
