OL,3,CGuernsey will not send national
OL,4,Cfootball teams to the Island Games
OL,6,FThe GFA Board concluded that the type
OL,7,Fof accommodation provided, the
OL,8,Finability to meet safeguarding
OL,9,Fmeasures, and the mixed ages of
OL,10,Fplayers made Guernsey's participation
OL,11,F"unviable".
OL,13,FGary adds: "We know this will come as
OL,14,Fa huge disappointment to the players
OL,15,Fbut the GFA will be actively looking
OL,16,Ffor alternative opportunities for off-
OL,17,Fisland competition during 2025."
